<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Feature which allows translate all recaptcha elements is described on <a href="http://code.google.com/apis/recaptcha/docs/customization.html">http://code.google.com/apis/recaptcha/…</a> .
But following code do not set custom_translation option:
$captchaEngine = new Zend_Captcha_ReCaptcha();
        $captchaEngine-&gt;setPubkey($config-&gt;recaptcha-&gt;public_key);
        $captchaEngine-&gt;setPrivkey($config-&gt;recaptcha-&gt;private_key);
        $captchaEngine-&gt;setOption('theme', 'white');</p>

<pre><code>    $customTranslations = '{instructions_visual : \'Wpisz dwa wyrazy:\', instructions_audio: \'Wpisz usłyszany tekst:\'}';

    $captchaEngine-&gt;setOption('custom_translations', $customTranslations);
</code></pre>

